description: Finally it was snowing over the last couple of days here in Prague. So I went out to find somebody to play some crazy games with me. I met a guy with a strange accent. Don´t get me wrong - his Czech was not bad - but I just realized that he was not from here. Actually he was from Russia. A small guy. But like many Russian he agreed to do something stupid in the snow to show the strength of his body. I offered him 3,000 crowns to undress and jump into the snow buck naked. As you might imagine he was almost freezing afterwards. So I invited him to come with me to a little hotel. There he could get a hot shower and the possibility to make even more money. *evil grin*
title: Czech Hunter 126
